#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.85"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.85:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.85:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga"
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.85:0.3"
msgid "85. Katthīsutta"
msgstr "85. A Boaster"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā mahācundo cetīsu viharati sahajātiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Mahācunda was staying in the land of the Cetis at "
"Sahajāti."

msgctxt "an10.85:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā mahācundo bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There he addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an10.85:1.3"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhave”ti."
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!”"

msgctxt "an10.85:1.4"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato mahācundassa paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied."

msgctxt "an10.85:1.5"
msgid "Āyasmā mahācundo etadavoca:"
msgstr "Venerable Mahācunda said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.158"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāvuso, bhikkhu katthī hoti vikatthī adhigamesu:"
msgstr "“Take a mendicant who boasts and brags about their achievements:"

msgctxt "an10.85:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ "
"samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, "
"ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ "
"samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpajjāmipi "
"vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I enter and emerge from the first absorption, the second absorption, the "
"third absorption, and the fourth absorption. And I enter and emerge from the "
"dimensions of infinite space, infinite consciousness, nothingness, and "
"neither perception nor non-perception. And I enter and emerge from the "
"cessation of perception and feeling.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ tathāgato vā tathāgatasāvako vā jhāyī samāpattikusalo "
"paracittakusalo paracittapariyāyakusalo samanuyuñjati samanuggāhati "
"samanubhāsati."
msgstr ""
"They’re pursued, pressed, and grilled by the Realized One, or by one of his "
"disciples who has the absorptions, and is skilled in attainments, in the "
"minds of others, and in the ways of another’s mind."

msgctxt "an10.85:3.2"
msgid ""
"So tathāgatena vā tathāgatasāvakena vā jhāyinā samāpattikusalena "
"paracittakusalena paracittapariyāyakusalena samanuyuñjiyamāno "
"samanuggāhiyamāno samanubhāsiyamāno irīṇaṃ āpajjati vicinaṃ āpajjati anayaṃ "
"āpajjati byasanaṃ āpajjati anayabyasanaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"Grilled in this way they get stuck or lose their way. They come to ruin and "
"disaster."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:4.1"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ tathāgato vā tathāgatasāvako vā jhāyī samāpattikusalo "
"paracittakusalo paracittapariyāyakusalo evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca manasi "
"karoti:"
msgstr ""
"The Realized One or one of his disciples comprehends their mind and "
"investigates:"

msgctxt "an10.85:4.2"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu kho ayamāyasmā katthī hoti vikatthī adhigamesu—"
msgstr ""
"‘Why does this venerable boast and brag about their achievements, saying:"

msgctxt "an10.85:4.3"
msgid "ahaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi … pe …"
msgstr "“I enter and emerge from the first absorption …"

msgctxt "an10.85:4.4"
msgid "ahaṃ saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipī’ti."
msgstr "and the cessation of perception and feeling.”’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:5.1"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ tathāgato vā tathāgatasāvako vā jhāyī samāpattikusalo "
"paracittakusalo paracittapariyāyakusalo evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāti:"
msgstr "They understand:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:6.1"
msgid ""
"‘Dīgharattaṃ kho ayamāyasmā khaṇḍakārī chiddakārī sabalakārī kammāsakārī na "
"santatakārī na santatavutti sīlesu."
msgstr ""
"‘For a long time this venerable’s deeds have been corrupt, flawed, "
"blemished, and tainted. Their deeds and behavior are inconsistent."

msgctxt "an10.85:6.2"
msgid "Dussīlo kho ayamāyasmā."
msgstr "This venerable is unethical,"

msgctxt "an10.85:6.3"
msgid "Dussilyaṃ kho pana tathāgatappavedite dhammavinaye parihānametaṃ. (1)"
msgstr ""
"and unethical conduct means decline in the teaching and training proclaimed "
"by the Realized One."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:7.1"
msgid "Assaddho kho pana ayamāyasmā;"
