#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.160"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:16.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, sahāyako sahāyakaṃ evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Suppose one friend was to say to another:"

#. VAR: dhanena → bandho (mr)
#. VAR: assa, yāceyyāsi maṃ → yācissasi maṃ (bj, pts1) | pavedeyyāsi maṃ (s1-3) | parājeyyāpi maṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an10.85:16.2"
msgid ""
"‘yadā te, samma, dhanena dhanakaraṇīyaṃ assa, yāceyyāsi maṃ dhanaṃ. Dassāmi "
"te dhanan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘My dear friend, when you need money for some payment, just ask me and I’ll "
"give it.’"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.3"
msgid ""
"So kiñcideva dhanakaraṇīye samuppanne sahāyako sahāyakaṃ evaṃ vadeyya: ‘"
"attho me, samma, dhanena. Dehi me dhanan’ti."
msgstr ""
"Then when some payment falls due, that friend says to their friend: ‘I need "
"some money, my dear friend. Give me some.’"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.4"
msgid "So evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "They’d say:"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.5"
msgid "‘tena hi, samma, idha khanāhī’ti. So tatra khananto nādhigaccheyya."
msgstr ""
"‘Well then, my dear friend, dig here.’ So they dig there, but don’t find "
"anything."

msgctxt "an10.85:16.6"
msgid "So evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "They’d say:"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.7"
msgid "‘alikaṃ maṃ, samma, avaca; tucchakaṃ maṃ, samma, avaca—idha khanāhī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘You lied to me, my dear friend, you spoke baselessly when you told me to "
"dig here.’"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.8"
msgid "So evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "They’d say:"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.9"
msgid ""
"‘nāhaṃ taṃ, samma, alikaṃ avacaṃ, tucchakaṃ avacaṃ. Tena hi, samma, idha "
"khanāhī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘My dear friend, I didn’t lie or speak baselessly. Well then, dig here.’"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.10"
msgid "So tatrapi khananto nādhigaccheyya."
msgstr "So they dig there as well, but don’t find anything."

msgctxt "an10.85:16.11"
msgid "So evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "They’d say:"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.12"
msgid "‘alikaṃ maṃ, samma, avaca, tucchakaṃ maṃ, samma, avaca—idha khanāhī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘You lied to me, my dear friend, you spoke baselessly when you said dig "
"here.’"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.13"
msgid "So evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "They’d say:"

msgctxt "an10.85:16.14"
msgid ""
"‘nāhaṃ taṃ, samma, alikaṃ avacaṃ, tucchakaṃ avacaṃ. Tena hi, samma, idha "
