"samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpajjāmipi "
"vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipi, ahaṃ "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajjāmipi vuṭṭhahāmipī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I enter and emerge from the first absorption … and the cessation of "
"perception and feeling.’"

