#. <a class="sc" id="sc31"></a>
msgctxt "an10.85:31.1"
msgid ""
"So vatāvuso, bhikkhu ‘ime dasa dhamme appahāya imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ "
"virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
